# Stage 1 chat and dataset lifecycle

Stage 1 must move toward:
- one active dataset at a time
- chat-first UI
- chat_id and dataset_id boundaries
- no mixing old chat context with new datasets
- old chats should become archive/read-only once dataset changes

Until full lifecycle is implemented:
- do not introduce UI behavior that assumes multiple active datasets
- do not continue old chat context across dataset changes
- prefer simple and explicit dataset status over hidden logic